OL,5, An inquest into the death of a head    
OL,6, teacher has heard how she felt         
OL,7, "powerless" after her school was       
OL,8, inspected by Ofsted.                   
OL,10,FRuth Perry told her husband Jonathan   
OL,11,Fshe believed her career could be over, 
OL,12,Fon the first day of the inspection at  
OL,13,FCaversham Primary in November 2022.    
OL,15,FMrs Perry, who had been head teacher   
OL,16,Ffor 13 years, took her own life in     
OL,17,FJanuary while awaiting Ofsted's report.
OL,19,FOfsted downgraded the school to        
OL,20,Finadequate after the visit.            
